{"tid":2100503,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中環空置率見海嘯後新高","createTime":"2020-07-09T05:51:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T07:48:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4431f9fdc7c3b53346dfb48625174cd3c53fe1e6","tid":2100503,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T05:51:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200709/RUD4VKIRO7GPRORZ5T6CJPMKGE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200709%2FRUD4VKIRO7GPRORZ5T6CJPMKGE%2F&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmmWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=0824a854\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200709%2FRUD4VKIRO7GPRORZ5T6CJPMKGE%2F&h=8b82b863\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200709/RUD4VKIRO7GPRORZ5T6CJPMKGE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中環空置率見海嘯後新高<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/UGPTcL-QS5HjEBQqEyzQFdDNF34=/640x437/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DJHI37YUK72JVHNQL3MFZ5VW3Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUGPTcL-QS5HjEBQqEyzQFdDNF34%3D%2F640x437%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDJHI37YUK72JVHNQL3MFZ5VW3Y.jpg&h=951f90bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中環甲級寫字樓市場5月錄115,600方呎負吸納量。<br />\n<br />\n本地武漢肺炎疫情有反彈迹象，經濟復蘇恐再受影響，商廈交投持續低迷；不少大型公司更轉租非核心區商廈，拖累傳統商業區甲級商廈租金顯著向下。<br />\n<br />\n仲量聯行《香港地產市場觀察》指出，上月中環甲級寫字樓空置率升至5%，按月再升0.4%，為2008年金融海嘯後最高，導致租金下跌2.7%至平均每方呎102.4元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩金融機構寧落戶銅鑼灣<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：學者：外企來港投資意欲低<br />\n<br />\n研究部資料顯示，上月整體寫字樓租金按月跌2.2%，5月尖沙嘴及九龍東空置率分別升至6.5%及13.7%，整體空置率微升0.2個百分點至7.4%。<br />\n<br />\n仲量聯行大中華<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n的負吸納量，為一年多以來的按月最高數字。<br />\n<br />\n商廈新租賃成交，現時主要集中於中環<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n鑼灣利園三期，合共承租該廈18,900方呎的樓面。<br />\n<br />\n另外，美國銀行中心今年2月錄得一<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n出，呎租約46元，創該廈三年以來新低。"},{"pid":"89a15ee0140c1af3603d127471c9a04a73583c63","tid":2100503,"uid":134415,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T06:05:03.000Z","msg":"改裝成住宅包佢炒上5萬蚊呎"},{"pid":"a1e905de7b551f64cbf25c8e8635cf103f5199a7","tid":2100503,"uid":85629,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T06:06:29.000Z","msg":"只要祖國一堆公司來港上市<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即時fully occupier"},{"pid":"8551aec992ba6fd006d5a34c966f0905f1053f9e","tid":2100503,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1e905de7b551f64cbf25c8e8635cf103f5199a7","tid":2100503,"uid":85629,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T06:06:29.000Z","msg":"只要祖國一堆公司來港上市<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即時fully occupier"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T06:06:42.000Z","msg":"Occupied*"},{"pid":"69690de1547d978198b0677552b695f7716b276b","tid":2100503,"uid":191926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a1e905de7b551f64cbf25c8e8635cf103f5199a7","tid":2100503,"uid":85629,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T06:06:29.000Z","msg":"只要祖國一堆公司來港上市<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即時fully occupier"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T06:07:25.000Z","msg":"強國辦公室空置率 去到 3x%<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b2b6fa3b515a225d841808d0da2f56e9cc422d","tid":2100503,"uid":4811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T06:08:05.000Z","msg":"政苦：我睇唔到、無乜凸別"},{"pid":"2bc000f45db80d419d6a9ebd1ed24837d0611478","tid":2100503,"uid":50101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1e905de7b551f64cbf25c8e8635cf103f5199a7","tid":2100503,"uid":85629,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T06:06:29.000Z","msg":"只要祖國一堆公司來港上市<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即時fully occupier"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi